[
  {
    "startTime": 0.04,
    "endTime": 2.54,
    "text": "On the show, you are a couple."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.55,
    "endTime": 8.74,
    "text": "People seem to root for you as a couple, and you guys play it up in public, even though you're not romantically linked."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.75,
    "endTime": 9.5,
    "text": "Yes, you do!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.7,
    "endTime": 11.0,
    "text": "Oh, stop it Conan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.0,
    "endTime": 14.65,
    "text": "Yes. You do, you like walk around, you'll, you'll..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.66,
    "endTime": 16.97,
    "text": "I've seen pictures of you where you're holding hands."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.97,
