    "text": "It's like you're taunting the photographers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.8,
    "endTime": 20.400000000000002,
    "text": "No, we're linking arms."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.4,
    "endTime": 24.0,
    "text": "Linking arms, holding hands. It's the same thing!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.0,
    "endTime": 26.95,
    "text": "And it sickens me, you young people."
