  {
    "startTime": 28.0,
    "endTime": 31.15,
    "text": "Now, your fans are very serious, also very creative."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.18,
    "endTime": 34.0,
    "text": "So, they refer to Glenn and Maggie a lot as \"Gleggie.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.2,
    "endTime": 35.900000000000006,
    "text": "Which sounds like a disease."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.97,
    "endTime": 39.0,
    "text": "Yeah, it's like, it sounds like the Scottish word for phlegm. You know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.0,
    "endTime": 40.0,
    "text": "It's like a..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.4,
    "endTime": 41.4,
    "text": "You know, it has a..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.6,
    "endTime": 42.6,
    "text": "It's a throw up sound."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.66,
    "endTime": 44.529999999999994,
    "text": "It's a throw up onomatopoeia."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.54,
    "endTime": 47.0,
    "text": "It's like ralphing, or like..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.28,
    "endTime": 48.5,
    "text": "Do you like the name \"Gleggie?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.5,
    "endTime": 53.39,
    "text": "Are you guys okay with that? As being the both of you as human beings being referred to jointly as \"Gleggie.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.4,
    "endTime": 57.0,
    "text": "The alternative we realized is \"Mann.\" Is it? \"Mann.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.2,
    "endTime": 58.830000000000005,
    "text": "\"Mann\" is good, with two 'n's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.84,
    "endTime": 60.540000000000006,
    "text": "Oh, \"Mann?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.55,
    "endTime": 61.26,
    "text": "That's good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.27,
    "endTime": 63.6,
    "text": "Okay. I guess that works."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.6,
    "endTime": 64.05,
    "text": "Alright."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.06,
    "endTime": 65.16,
    "text": "It makes no sense to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.17,
    "endTime": 66.82000000000001,
    "text": "No, I think \"Gleggie\" is better."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.82,
    "endTime": 67.63999999999999,
    "text": "\"Gleggie\" is good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.65,
    "endTime": 69.9,
    "text": "\"Gleggie,\" \"Gleggie,\" \"Gleggie.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.93,
    "endTime": 70.60000000000001,
    "text": "Oh, I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.629,
    "endTime": 71.56,
    "text": "Do you have another one?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.57,
    "endTime": 73.0,
    "text": "I don't know what else it could be."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.16,
    "endTime": 75.19,
    "text": "I think it should be nothing to do with either one of our names."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.19,
    "endTime": 77.0,
    "text": "It should just be like..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.0,
    "endTime": 78.46,
    "text": "Yeah, those two."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.47,
    "endTime": 79.61,
    "text": "Those two, those two."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.62,
    "endTime": 81.0,
    "text": "Andy and I together are \"Conandy.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.33,
    "endTime": 84.36,
    "text": "Or candy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.37,
