  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.44,
    "endTime": 92.16,
    "text": "Oh. That was good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.17,
    "endTime": 94.96000000000001,
    "text": "Like a song."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.64,
    "endTime": 96.21,
    "text": "Nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.22,
    "endTime": 98.0,
    "text": "Let's change topics."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.0,
    "endTime": 103.03,
    "text": "On the show, it was a big moment when you guys had your first kiss."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.03,
    "endTime": 103.96000000000001,
    "text": "Huge moment."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.97,
    "endTime": 110.06,
    "text": "And we actually have a still from that moment, when your characters first kiss."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.44,
    "endTime": 114.96,
    "text": "Now, Steven, let's talk about your technique."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.53,
    "endTime": 119.31,
    "text": "Steven, do you see anything wrong there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.74,
    "endTime": 123.05,
    "text": "Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 127.03,
    "text": "It's pretty on point to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.04,
    "endTime": 129.0,
    "text": "Yeah, pretty on point. Is that..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.0,
    "endTime": 135.86,
    "text": "Now, I'm hoping that's not your, in your private life, your technique that you keep your eyes open while you're kissing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.34,
    "endTime": 137.75,
    "text": "Okay, this is the thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.76,
    "endTime": 145.26999999999998,
    "text": "In that moment, Glenn is confused because he's like, this beautiful woman is about to kiss me for, like, just being here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.28,
    "endTime": 151.51,
    "text": "And so it's a shock to him, and he keeps his eyes open to make sure he takes all of it in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.7,
    "endTime": 156.7,
    "text": "He's a participant and an observer at the same time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.3,
    "endTime": 164.0,
    "text": "He's just an efficient guy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.0,
    "endTime": 168.17,
    "text": "Yeah, but if you had opened your eyes, there would have been no second kiss."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.18,
    "endTime": 170.0,
    "text": "What're you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.0,
    "endTime": 175.66,
    "text": "I mean the guy is just like there, like, I am a participant and an observer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.44,
    "endTime": 178.42,
    "text": "That's not creating a romantic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.43,
    "endTime": 184.0,
    "text": "And at the end, when I say to you, \"Were your eyes open?\" and you said no, now I know you're lying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.0,
    "endTime": 186.0,
    "text": "My bad."
  }
]